 
NOTE: To set install prefix add PREFIX=<your install prefix> as option when running sh_make
### BUILDING ###

0 . cd $extract_root
1 . cd src
2 . sh_make -f sh_makefile


### INSTALLING ###

1 . with installer
  1. sh_make DESTDIR=../pkg -f sh_makefile install # set PREFIX if needed
  3. sh_make -f sh_makefile installer
  2. /bin/sh install.sh  --prefix <prefix> # replace prefix with your install prefix

2. without
  1. sh_make -f sh_makefile install
  